OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'remarkable' man
OL,4,Cand his dog who died in crash
OL,6,FTributes are being paid to a
OL,7,F"remarkable" man and his dog, who died
OL,8,Ffollowing a crash on the Isle of Wight.
OL,10,FPaul Hart, 42, died when a blue Mazda
OL,11,F6 collided with a tree on Calbourne
OL,12,FRoad in Newport.
OL,14,FPolice were called to the scene at
OL,15,Fabout 10.10pm on Sunday 7 April.
OL,17,FPaul was found with serious injuries
OL,18,Fand died at the scene. His dog,
OL,19,FBailey, was also in the car and was
OL,20,Ftaken to an emergency vet, but had to
OL,21,Fbe put down due to its injuries.
