OL,6,FPaul's family have paid tribute to
OL,7,Fhim, saying: "It is with profound
OL,8,Fsadness that we announce the passing
OL,9,Fof a remarkable young man, Paul
OL,10,FAnthony Hart, whose life was
OL,11,Ftragically cut short along with his
OL,12,Flovely dog Bailey.
OL,14,F"His vibrant spirit, infectious
OL,15,Flaughter, and boundless energy touched
OL,16,Fthe lives of all who knew him.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
