OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'remarkable' man
OL,4,Cand his dog who died in crash
OL,6,F"He was a beacon of hope, a source of
OL,7,Finspiration and a testament of
OL,8,Fresilience in the face of adversity.
OL,9,FHis life, though brief, was a
OL,10,Ftestament to the power of love he gave.
OL,12,F"The world has lost a kind, caring,
OL,13,Finfectious and joyful man. We are
OL,14,Fproud to have given this gift to all
OL,15,Fwho knew him.
