OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to 'remarkable' man
OL,4,Cand his dog who died in crash
OL,6,F"In his memory, let us remember not
OL,7,Fjust the sorrow of his loss, but the
OL,8,Fjoy and love he brought into our
OL,9,Flives. Let us honour his legacy by
OL,10,Fliving our lives with the same
OL,11,Fpassion, kindness and generosity that
OL,12,Fhe demonstrated every day.
OL,14,F"We have been overwhelmed and humbled
OL,15,Fby the outpouring of support and would
OL,16,Flike to send a special thank you to
OL,17,Fall the tireless efforts made by all
OL,18,Fthe emergency services throughout this
OL,19,Fprocess. Those we love don't go away,
OL,20,Fthey walk beside us every day.
